snippet.title: New GitHub feature: the PR overview button
snippet.description:
There’s a new feature in GitHub pull requests that saves you from constant context switching. In the "new experience" view, you can now use the Overview button to see proposed changes without leaving your current tab. Check it out and let us know what you think!

Read more: https://github.blog/changelog

#PullRequest #PR #GitHub

About GitHub
It’s where over 180 million developers create, share, and ship the best code possible. It’s a place for anyone, from anywhere, to build anything—it’s where the world builds software. https://github.com
